{"tid":433875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瓦努阿圖：移民申請數Bitcoin   42個COIN就可移民取國籍","createTime":"2017-10-12T18:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T19:06:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c648d52e55b16ee433fa501c91928871efe1e60d","tid":433875,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，港人想去的地南太平洋島國瓦努阿圖，宣佈接受比特幣Bitcoin支付投資移民，換言之只需40多個比特幣，就可以買到一個國籍。<br />\n<br />\n瓦努阿圖此舉是全球首個可以接受比特幣購買國籍的國家，根據瓦努阿圖20萬美元移民經費作計算，比特幣境外現價報逾4,800美元，故以42個比特幣，就可以移民到這個快樂的國度。<br />\n<br />\n雖然中國禁比特幣交易後，曾令其價格一沉。不過，自日前突破4,600美元後，昨日一度升至4,854美元的逾1個月高位，急挫後收復失地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171012/20179962?_ga=2.59865645.1093218303.1507735960-7797648.1439036704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171012%2F20179962%3F_ga%3D2.59865645.1093218303.1507735960-7797648.1439036704&d=sU61sAx2fcf5rzR%2Bp6lq8ZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=c764d5b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171012%2F20179962%3F_ga%3D2.59865645.1093218303.1507735960-7797648.1439036704&h=c2ec0b40\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171012/20179962?_ga=2.59865645.1093218303.1507735960-7797648.1439036704</a>"},{"pid":"fe36c89a6b6b173bb7d12d496ec238366a5f506d","tid":433875,"uid":128229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n百幾萬我都移民到台灣<br />\n點會去咁既垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84511584cf1dd4a1a4cc15c812ddd0de6ff3e57","tid":433875,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:18:08.000Z","msg":